{
  "meta": {
    "is_partial": true,
    "description": "모바일용 상품 가격 표시"
  },
  "type": "basic",
  "name": "Div",
  "children": [
    {
      "comment": "할인 전 금액 (취소선, 할인 있을 때)",
      "type": "basic",
      "name": "Div",
      "if": "{{product.data?.discount_rate > 0}}",
      "props": { "className": "mb-1" },
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "basic",
          "name": "Span",
          "props": { "className": "text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 line-through" },
          "text": "{{product.data?.multi_currency_list_price?.[_global.preferredCurrency ?? 'KRW']?.formatted ?? product.data?.list_price_formatted}}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "comment": "할인율 + 판매가 (할인 있을 때)",
      "type": "basic",
      "name": "Div",
      "if": "{{product.data?.discount_rate > 0}}",
      "props": { "className": "flex items-center gap-2" },
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "basic",
          "name": "Span",
          "props": { "className": "text-lg font-bold text-red-500" },
          "text": "{{product.data?.discount_rate}}%"
        },
        {
          "type": "basic",
          "name": "Span",
          "props": { "className": "text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white" },
          "text": "{{product.data?.multi_currency_selling_price?.[_global.preferredCurrency ?? 'KRW']?.formatted ?? product.data?.selling_price_formatted}}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "comment": "판매가 (할인 없을 때)",
      "type": "basic",
      "name": "Div",
      "if": "{{!product.data?.discount_rate || product.data?.discount_rate <= 0}}",
      "props": { "className": "text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white" },
      "text": "{{product.data?.multi_currency_selling_price?.[_global.preferredCurrency ?? 'KRW']?.formatted ?? product.data?.selling_price_formatted}}"
    },
    {
      "comment": "배송 불가 사전 경고 (B8 — 선택 배송국가로 배송 불가, 모바일 가격 영역)",
      "type": "basic",
      "name": "Div",
      "if": "{{product.data?.is_shippable_to_selected_country === false}}",
      "props": { "className": "flex items-center gap-1.5 mt-1.5" },
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "basic",
          "name": "Icon",
          "props": { "name": "triangle-exclamation", "size": "sm", "className": "text-red-500 dark:text-red-400 shrink-0" }
        },
        {
          "type": "basic",
          "name": "Span",
          "props": { "className": "text-sm font-medium text-red-600 dark:text-red-400" },
          "text": "$t:shop.shippability.not_shippable"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
